            <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear());</script> What Eat Today |
            Webapplication 204359 &nbsp;&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-heart-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> <br /><br /><br />
        </center>
    </div>
</div>

	